metadata.name: DickToad #1
metadata.description: DickToadz is a community-driven project based on CryptoDickbutts and CrypToadz by Gremplin NFT projects.  As super-fans of the original projects, we set out to build an experience like no other: create your own DickToadz or ToadButts by selecting all of your own custom layers. DickToadz is a 5,200 sized collection for mint + 69 1/1 pieces for post-mint airdropping, making it a total 5,269 NFT collection
